Message: Hi, I’m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?
The user completes the submission of the form

Hello. One friend who runs Home improvement agency recomenned me NewsBreak. I really want to try it out! Our team had experience to run taboola and outbrain in the past ( succsessfullly)  so I think it's important to try NewsBreal as well. Do we have account manager? Is there any way to speak to someone to get good intro etc?

Thanks for your interest in NewsBreak! At this time, dedicated account management is reserved for advertisers who meet a daily spend threshold of $1,000 or more. If you’re not at that level yet, no worries — our self-serve platform has everything you need to launch and optimize your campaigns successfully. Our support team is also available via chat or email if you need any help. In the meantime, feel free to check out our Help Center — it’s a great resource for quick answers if you don’t need to reach out to support directly. And don’t forget to subscribe to our email updates and keep an eye out for our monthly webinar training sessions! Let us know if you’d like assistance getting started.
